title: wikispeedia_speed_limits_must_show_tags.sqlite3.tgz
description:
Road Speed Limit database from Wikispeedia.org.

Contains speed limits worldwide.

Gathered by over 600 volunteers.

Join us. We pay contributors. Its your gas, so you should get paid.

Since 2005, Wikispeedia.org has been giving out speed limit information free of charge. We help people reduce road rage with smart cruise controls. No one at Wikispeedia has ever received any salary or payment. 

The data is sqlite3 format. To unpack use "tar -xzvf file.tgz"

API: see wikispeedia.org
